ADD COLUMN documentType ENUM('cpf', 'cnpj') DEFAULT 'cpf',
ADD COLUMN documentNumber VARCHAR(32),
ADD COLUMN pixKeyType ENUM('cpf', 'cnpj', 'email', 'phone', 'random'),
ADD COLUMN pixKey VARCHAR(256),
ADD COLUMN pixKeyHolderName VARCHAR(256),
ADD COLUMN pixKeyDocument VARCHAR(32),
ADD COLUMN pixKeyVerified TINYINT DEFAULT 0,
ADD COLUMN acceptedIntermediationTerms TINYINT DEFAULT 0,
ADD COLUMN acceptedPayoutTerms TINYINT DEFAULT 0,
ADD COLUMN acceptedContestationPolicy TINYINT DEFAULT 0,
ADD COLUMN termsAcceptedAt TIMESTAMP NULL;
